  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the effect of regular consumption of probiotic milk
      in preventing illnesses in Finnish children attending day care centres, and possible
      cost-benefits that could be associated with fewer illnesses.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
